14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 12 O.S. 2021, Section 1148.4, is
16 amended to read as follows:
17 Section 1148.4. The summons shall be issued and returned as in
18 other cases, except that it shall command the sheriff, or other
19 person serving it, to summon the defendant to appear for trial at
20 the time and place specified therein, which time shall be not less
21 than five (5) days nor more than ten (10) days nor more than fifteen
22 (15) days from the date that the summons is issued; provided,
23 however, a trial for an action pursuant to subsection C or D of
24 Section 132 of Title 41 of the Oklahoma Statutes shall be not less
