1 subs equent action for the payment of rent. A judgment for forcible
2 entry and detainer shall not preclude the property owner from
3 pursuing a subsequent action for other monetary relief. Such
4 service shall not be rendered ineffectual by the failure of the
5 defendant to actually see or receive such posted process nor by the
